{"tid":1306013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從錯誤中學習，由光復上水重新上路","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:20:40.000Z","uid":156914,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c0afbf36a63c3f2e26f6f26edaba598fd75343","tid":1306013,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"錯就要認！失焦左係無可爭議嘅事實，所以我地更加要放眼未來，唔好再糾結係呢一刻嘅錯誤決定上面。<br />\n<br />\n依家大家士氣咁差，就正好靠光復上水打支強心針，重振旗鼓<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次光復上水一定要多人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有，唔好忘記五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"9f5d34a03cd8d649dbafa673a857e7f0b7045d7f","tid":1306013,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"[7.13 光復上水] 快入TG channel睇行動詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305853</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"61d88657759519795d91568933220ee107874f0a","tid":1306013,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=cc0195c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=0c392ec0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">6.12一周月行動</span> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3